  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested information about special pricing for students and nonprofits for Manus AI. Assistant explained inability to provide pricing information and redirected to official support channels at help.manus.im.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser seeking cost-effective access to Manus AI through educational or nonprofit discounts\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nAssistant politely declined to provide pricing information and provided proper support channel referral\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [referral] support_redirect — Directed user to help.manus.im for pricing inquiries\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Maintained boundaries around pricing information\n- Provided appropriate support channel\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Clear boundary communication\n- Helpful redirection to proper channels\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Users seek educational/nonprofit pricing options\n\n## Challenges & Blockers\n\n- Assistant cannot access or provide pricing information\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- What discount programs actually exist for students/nonprofits?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- User should contact help.manus.im for pricing information\n---\nUID: jcSpm9oczPTvJdRg8vWzoW | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0082\n"
